<html>
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
	<style type="text/css">
		body{background-color:#1A4D9E;}
		#contentTable{border:0px none #000000;margin-top:10px;}
		.defaultText{font-size:14px;color:#333333;line-height:125%;font-family:Verdana;width:600px;background-color:#B5C5DD;padding:20px;}
		.backgroundTable{background-color:#1A4D9E;}
	</style>
</head>

<body leftmargin="0" marginwidth="0" topmargin="0" marginheight="0" offset="0" style="background-color: #1A4D9E;">

	<table width="100%" cellpadding="10" cellspacing="0" class="backgroundTable" style="background-color: #1A4D9E;">
		<tr>
			<td valign="top" align="center">
				<div style="text-align: left;">
					<a href="http://www.linguazone.com" style="color: #800000;text-decoration: underline;font-weight: normal;">
						<img src="http://linguazone.s3.amazonaws.com/images/newsletter/header.jpg" alt="LinguaZone.com: customized online teaching tools and games" border="0" style="margin: 0; padding: 0;" />
					</a>
				</div>
			</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td valign="top" align="center">
				<table id="contentTable" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="600" style="border: 0px none #000000;margin-top: 10px;">
					<tr>
						<td valign="top" class="defaultText" align="left" style="font-size: 14px;color: #333333;line-height: 125%;font-family: Verdana;width: 600px;background-color: #B5C5DD;padding: 20px;">

					<p>
						Dear <%= @user.first_name %>,
					</p>

					<p>
						Your subscription to <a href="www.linguazone.com">LinguaZone.com</a> is coming up for <strong>renewal in 2 weeks</strong>. We hope that you have enjoyed using the games, word lists, and audio blogs this year.
					</p>
					<p>
						We also hope that you will renew your subscription for another year as we look to the improvements and additions that are coming in the days and months ahead. Login to your account, then scroll to the bottom of the <strong>Overview page</strong> for instructions on how to  renew your subscription for another 12 months. Your invoice will be emailed to you for payment by check or purchase order.
					</p>

					<p>
						If you have any questions about renewing your subscription or about changing subscription plans, please reply to this email (info@linguazone.com) or call us directly at 610.322.9137.
					</p>

					<p>
						many thanks for your continued support,<br />
						Colin Angevine and Margaret Roberts<br />
						LinguaZone.com
					</p>
					
					
						</td>
					</tr>
				</table>
			</td>
		</tr>
	</table>
</body>
</html>